OL,3,C'Heroic' crane driver who saved man
OL,4,Cfrom burning building dies
OL,6,FA crane driver who was hailed as
OL,7,F"heroic" for taking swift action to
OL,8,Frescue a man from a burning tower
OL,9,Fblock has died.
OL,11,FGlen Edwards was working at the
OL,12,FStation Hill development, in Reading,
OL,13,FBerkshire, when the fire took hold in
OL,14,FNovember 2023.
OL,16,FThe charity Bucket List Wishes reached
OL,17,Fout to help Mr Edwards after he was
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with spine cancer last year,
OL,19,Fand said, in a social media post, that
OL,20,Fit was "utterly heartbroken" to share
OL,21,Fnews of his death.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
