OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775052666
OL,3,C'Heroic' crane driver who saved man
OL,4,Cfrom burning building dies
OL,6,FIt described Mr Edwards as a "very
OL,7,Fspecial man" and "local hero", adding:
OL,8,F"It was truly an honour & a real joy
OL,9,Ffor us to know him."
OL,11,FMr Edwards had previously been
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with tongue cancer, which
OL,13,Fwas successfully treated, although it
OL,14,Flater returned and spread to his spine.
OL,16,FAt an awards ceremony in Reading, Mr
OL,17,FEdwards and his wife met Gini Hackett,
OL,18,Fthe founder of Bucket List Wishes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
