OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775052666
OL,3,C'Heroic' crane driver who saved man
OL,4,Cfrom burning building dies
OL,6,FShe heard Mr Edwards had been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with terminal cancer and
OL,8,Foffered to fulfil his dream wishlist.
OL,10,FBut rather than ask for an exotic
OL,11,Fholiday or lavish cruise, Mr Edwards
OL,12,Fneeded to move home and instead asked
OL,13,Ffor some new flooring and house
OL,14,Ffurnishings.
OL,16,FFootage of Mr Edwards' daring rescue
OL,17,Fmission at the Station Development
OL,18,Ffire was captured by bystanders, who
OL,19,Ferupted into applause at his actions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
