OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775052666
OL,3,C'Heroic' crane driver who saved man
OL,4,Cfrom burning building dies
OL,6,FMore than 50 firefighters were sent to
OL,7,Ftackle the fire, which led to the
OL,8,Fevacuation of hundreds of construction
OL,9,Fworkers and office staff from
OL,10,Fsurrounding buildings.
OL,12,FAs smoke and flames engulfed the high-
OL,13,Frise building, Mr Edwards spotted the
OL,14,Fconstruction worker trapped on its
OL,15,Froof and took immediate action to
OL,16,Frescue him.
OL,18,FHe used all of his 30-years experience
OL,19,Fas a crane driver to manoeuvre his
OL,20,Fcrane over the roof.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775052666
OL,3,C'Heroic' crane driver who saved man
OL,4,Cfrom burning building dies
OL,6,FMr Edwards then lowered a cage, which
OL,7,Fwas used for transporting personnel,
OL,8,Fto the trapped worker, allowing him to
OL,9,Fclimb inside and be moved to safety.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian last year, Mr
OL,12,FEdwards described his recollections
OL,13,Ffrom that fateful day.
OL,15,F"The smoke was absolutely intense, I
OL,16,Fcould hardly see him, well, I couldn't
OL,17,Fsee him. I knew he was there, he was
OL,18,Fstanding on the edge of the building.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
