PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775052666
OL,3,C'Heroic' crane driver who saved man
OL,4,Cfrom burning building dies
OL,6,F"By the time I got the cradle on he
OL,7,Fhad about two metres of area he was
OL,8,Fstanding on that wasn't alight. The
OL,9,Fadrenalin was out the roof.
OL,11,F"He's got two girls, eight and 13 they
OL,12,Fwere at the time, and I got a very
OL,13,Fheartfelt letter that would bring a
OL,14,Ftear to your eye."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
